Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.88,0:04:46.64,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn萝莉体-DDC.yolan\fs20\bord0\c&H656F75&\frz355.2\pos(1178.667,445.999)}优酪乳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.88,0:04:46.64,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn萝莉体-DDC.yolan\fs20\bord0\c&H656F75&\frz355.2\pos(1056,463.333)}可丽饼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.88,0:04:46.64,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn萝莉体-DDC.yolan\fs20\bord0\c&H656F75&\frz355.2\pos(1185.334,503.333)}雪芭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.77,0:04:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,蛋糕不错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.14,0:04:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,水果挞和可丽饼也挺不错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.04,0:04:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,创新甜品啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.78,0:05:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,打扫辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这里打扫完以后  能打扫一下泡沫分离装置吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.14,0:05:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.70,0:05:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我等会要去找乌冬妹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.24,0:05:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,她答应了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  她说她会想一些好吃的甜品
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.41,0:05:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊  希望一切顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.31,0:05:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,乌冬妹  欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.81,0:05:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那么第一次甜品会议开始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.92,0:05:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我有A到G的方案  想先听哪个?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.32,0:05:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,一晚上你能想出这么多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.76,0:05:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那就从A开始按顺序吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.09,0:05:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那么开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A方案的菜单是  冲绳特制芭菲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.01,0:05:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,大量使用岛上的水果  冰冰甜甜的南方芭菲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.24,0:05:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,敬请享用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.12,0:05:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,芭菲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.43,0:05:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.13,0:06:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,在鱼缸前划一块作为咖啡区
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.83,0:06:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,放上藤条桌子和沙发
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.49,0:06:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,就是像海外度假胜地一样的超日常空间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.81,0:06:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为会很火爆的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.95,0:06:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,确实很能带动话题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.28,0:06:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,带动话题  人气提升  很多顾客过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.65,0:06:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这不错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.93,0:06:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,但是办一个咖啡店会不会太大阵仗了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.92,0:06:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有多少预算
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.66,0:06:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,5000日元
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.84,0:06:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,完全不够啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.37,0:06:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.78,0:06:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.11,0:06:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,考虑到各种现况  能实现的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.54,0:06:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里摆个摊  卖创新的冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.88,0:06:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉不错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.79,0:06:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,摊位可以找夏凛借
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.80,0:06:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得这是最现实的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.20,0:06:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.60,0:06:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那决定卖冰淇淋了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.75,0:06:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,决定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.08,0:06:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好  那么我们赶快出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.12,0:06:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,去哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.60,0:07:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,想要做冰淇淋  首先要吃冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.16,0:07:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,要吃哪个?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.16,0:07:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,真难选择
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.07,0:07:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,还是香草味吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.37,0:07:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我就要菠萝巧克力味
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.29,0:07:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,赤豆抹茶  牛油果果仁和芝士开心果
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.05,0:07:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.92,0:07:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.73,0:07:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,味道特别浓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.36,0:07:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,很复杂的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.58,0:07:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,坚果吃起来不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.82,0:07:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样  里面混了不只一种坚果啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.75,0:07:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,很热心于研究呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.54,0:07:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,她一直都是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.84,0:07:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,小学烹饪课上  乌冬妹的那个班用了很多点子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.50,0:07:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,做得跟店里卖的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.12,0:07:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,因为料理蕴含着无穷的可能性嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.29,0:07:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,即便用的是同样的食材
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.85,0:08:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,用不同的做法和调味料  味道可以完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.71,0:08:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,经过各种尝试后  做出意外的料理时
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.44,0:08:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,会有很大的幸福感呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.60,0:08:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,找乌冬妹真是找对人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.76,0:08:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,对于空空琉一生的请求
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.68,0:08:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我全都满足了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.10,0:08:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我倒是完全不记得了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.93,0:08:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托的一方是不会记得的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.36,0:08:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,没错没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.47,0:08:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,比如「乌冬妹  这是我一生的请求
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.03,0:08:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,借我橡皮擦吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.81,0:08:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,或是「陪我去厕所」之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.13,0:08:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那根本是滥用请求呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.12,0:08:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,才那点事有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.44,0:08:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那我再去两三间冰店晃晃再回家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.43,0:08:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,再见啰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.26,0:08:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  拜托你啰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.41,0:08:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也得回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.01,0:08:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.13,0:08:51.63,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn萝莉体-DDC.yolan\fs30\bord0\c&HF8F6F6&\pos(820,185.333)\frz1.772}开设Pensta帐号了!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.13,0:08:51.63,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn萝莉体-DDC.yolan\fs20\bord0\c&HF8F6F6&\pos(826.667,522)\frz360}关注者可免费任选一款配料!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.08,0:08:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Penstagram吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.85,0:08:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么怎么  有什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.11,0:09:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,最近每间水族馆都有经营社群网站
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.87,0:09:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想透过洞天水族馆办一个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.42,0:09:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,很方便啊  宣传也很容易
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.45,0:09:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,风花  你有用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.36,0:09:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然现在没有  但以前有用过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.25,0:09:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那你教教我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.65,0:09:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.96,0:09:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,洞天水族馆的独特魅力是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.98,0:09:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,只要把这个展现出来就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.02,0:09:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,洞天水族馆的独特魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.71,0:09:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  接下来是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.26,0:09:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是打工的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.48,0:09:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,大男人不用介意这种小事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.48,0:09:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我拒绝露脸…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.30,0:09:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,咦  帮帮忙嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.76,0:09:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,空空琉  在吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.28,0:09:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你也拍一下这孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.74,0:09:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  是躄鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.04,0:09:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的推  有够可爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.65,0:09:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  应该不错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.30,0:10:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,很棒的照片呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.01,0:10:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是…是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.83,0:10:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,再来如果有能体现馆内气氛的照片就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.69,0:10:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,气氛吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.45,0:10:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.58,0:10:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,是认识的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.97,0:10:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  是每年夏天都会来的熟客
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.60,0:10:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,每年…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.26,0:10:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,从我还小的时候就一直来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.37,0:10:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那么久以前就开始?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.60,0:10:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他肯定很喜欢水族馆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.77,0:10:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思  自制冰淇淋不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.81,0:10:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.11,0:10:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不行?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.85,0:10:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.84,0:10:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,冰淇淋制造许可?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.20,0:10:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.08,0:10:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,根据食品卫生法规定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.81,0:10:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,要在路边摊或室外贩售自制冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.17,0:11:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,要有「冰淇淋类制造许可」才行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.07,0:11:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你们有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.91,0:11:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.18,0:11:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不过只要申请就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.64,0:11:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,据说申请几乎过不了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.32,0:11:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,店面的话还好说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.87,0:11:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,但室外的话  做好卫生管理很困难
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.47,0:11:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.78,0:11:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,冰淇淋不行的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.82,0:11:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈  你知道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.32,0:11:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那是常识呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.55,0:11:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都觉得做餐饮很容易
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.67,0:11:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,但证照和许可没这么好拿唷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.51,0:11:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:31.33,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn萝莉体-DDC.yolan\fs35\fax0.3\bord0\c&H0A1947&\pos(584,112.667)\frz344.3}\大家最喜欢{\c&H2044EB&}♡{\c&H0A1947&}/
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:31.33,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn萝莉体-DDC.yolan\fs35\fax0.3\bord0\c&H0A1947&\frz345.9\pos(593.333,234)}炸乌尾冬仔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:31.33,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn萝莉体-DDC.yolan\fs35\fax0.3\bord0\c&H0A1947&\frz346.8\pos(574.667,419.333)}一份 400日元
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:31.33,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn萝莉体-DDC.yolan\fs35\fax0.3\bord0\c&H2058B3&\frz345.6\pos(937.333,190)}不知吃什么好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:31.33,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn萝莉体-DDC.yolan\fs28\fax0.3\bord0\c&H2058B3&\pos(988,279.334)\frz346}就来厨师创作餐吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:31.33,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn萝莉体-DDC.yolan\fs30\fax0.3\bord0\c&H153680&\pos(1004,510)\frz350.4}800日元
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.57,0:11:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,当然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.12,0:11:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这是吃进嘴里  关系到人命的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.46,0:11:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,阿姨  有没有其他可以拿到的许可?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.51,0:11:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这个嘛…刨冰如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.66,0:11:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,刨冰?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.81,0:11:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然也要许可
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.36,0:11:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但门槛应该没乳制品高唷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.11,0:11:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,乌冬妹?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.11,0:11:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我来做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.80,0:11:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在就回家研究刨冰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.43,0:11:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,店就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.97,0:11:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这我怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.27,0:12:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我说月美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.78,0:12:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,松松绵绵的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.13,0:12:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.21,0:12:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.21,0:12:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,在做刨冰前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.58,0:12:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,先把冰块放置于常温环境一会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.90,0:12:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,刨出来就松松绵绵的了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.44,0:12:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,真不愧是乌冬妹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.04,0:12:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,但做生意的时候也要用这台刨吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.73,0:12:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.24,0:12:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,夏凛正在帮我弄一台商用的来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.34,0:12:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,咦  空也你不吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.91,0:12:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我就算了  脑袋会痛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.08,0:12:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.14,0:12:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,对了  也做个烧酒刨冰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.24,0:12:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,如果冰融化了  就只是烧酒加水而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.21,0:12:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,驳回  上班期间你还想喝酒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.26,0:12:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.81,0:13:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.11,0:13:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,难得看到你一副苦瓜脸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.32,0:13:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,想不到挺无趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.27,0:13:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,哪里无趣?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.80,0:13:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,以你来说  这菜单太普通了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.32,0:13:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不过也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.88,0:13:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟刨冰能发挥的创意有限
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.27,0:13:20.90,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn萝莉体-DDC.yolan\fs42\fax0.3\bord0\c&H282629&\pos(901.334,474.001)\frz211.8}刨冰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.40,0:13:20.90,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn萝莉体-DDC.yolan\fs30\fax0.3\bord0\c&H282629&\frz207.3\pos(796.001,378.002)}草莓味
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.40,0:13:20.90,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn萝莉体-DDC.yolan\fs30\fax0.3\bord0\c&H282629&\frz206.2\pos(669.334,310.002)}芒果味
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.40,0:13:20.90,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn萝莉体-DDC.yolan\fs30\fax0.3\bord0\c&H282629&\pos(593.334,250.002)\frz204.4}柠檬味
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:20.90,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn萝莉体-DDC.yolan\fs30\fax0.3\bord0\c&H282629&\frz201.6\pos(501.334,200.669)}哈密瓜味
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:20.90,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn萝莉体-DDC.yolan\fs25\fax0.3\bord0\c&H282629&\frz198.9\pos(432.001,140.669)}弹珠汽水味
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:20.90,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn萝莉体-DDC.yolan\fs25\fax0.3\bord0\c&H282629&\frz198.9\pos(368.001,83.336)}葡萄味
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:20.90,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn萝莉体-DDC.yolan\fs25\fax0.3\bord0\c&H282629&\frz198.3\pos(330.668,28.669)}咖啡味
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.65,0:13:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,就算不是你  换个人也能做这些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.19,0:13:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那话什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.44,0:13:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然我并不喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.33,0:13:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,但你是怎么想出芒果炖肉这种料理的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.32,0:13:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.03,0:13:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,咦  今天还没开?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.82,0:13:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.88,0:13:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,乌冬妹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.83,0:13:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.14,0:13:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,店不开  你是在做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.61,0:13:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,当然是为明天做准备呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.15,0:13:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀  生物还真难画呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.80,0:14:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我一心想让刨冰店成功
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.32,0:14:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,所以想法太死板了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.91,0:14:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,应该更自由点才对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.28,0:14:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,机会难得
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.52,0:14:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我想让大家吃到只有洞天才有的刨冰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.99,0:14:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,然后这个就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.80,0:14:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  希望你们能帮我一起画
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.40,0:14:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,做正事尽真心  一切会顺利的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.08,0:14:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,千万拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.60,0:14:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.48,0:14:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,还好拿到了卫生所的许可
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.44,0:14:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  拿到许可就能放下点心了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.16,0:14:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,话说为什么连我们都被拉来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.43,0:14:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,别发牢骚了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.18,0:14:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我可是有得到馆长同意的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.26,0:15:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,空空琉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.93,0:15:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.36,0:15:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,感谢您每年都莅临本馆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.67,0:15:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,时间快到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.80,0:15:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.52,0:15:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我从报纸上得知了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.68,0:15:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,居然要结束营业  真是可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.76,0:15:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这件事还没完全定案
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.31,0:15:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.42,0:15:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我对这个地方有着很深厚的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.73,0:15:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,对洞天吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.15,0:15:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,很久以前  我很小的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.06,0:15:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥就去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.01,0:15:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我想替哥哥好好活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.02,0:15:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,长大之后自主创业  努力工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.00,0:16:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,但天不遂人愿  公司倒闭了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.64,0:16:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那时  我偶然来到了这座刚刚建成的水族馆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.38,0:16:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,居然在这里遇见了去世的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.47,0:16:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥鼓励了迷失方向的我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.25,0:16:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,并没有实际对话  只是我感受到了鼓舞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.26,0:16:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,但我因此重振旗鼓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.93,0:16:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,成功创立了新的公司
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.98,0:16:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,从那以后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.13,0:16:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,为了能再次见到哥哥  我每年都会来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.88,0:16:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不过直到今年也没能再会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.05,0:16:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉说了这么奇怪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.57,0:16:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不  非常感谢您如此看重这个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.05,0:16:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.10,0:16:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,珍贵而特别的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.68,0:18:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,明年请再来  我一定会办下去等您
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.41,0:18:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我会期待那一天的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.20,0:19:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,洞天水族馆是特别的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.96,0:19:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,有人也这样认为
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.49,0:19:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不只是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.30,0:19:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.56,0:19:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,周末限定  洞天水族馆特制原创刨冰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.13,0:19:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了  摊位摆好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.54,0:19:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,快累死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:23.22,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正粗圆_GBK\fs25\bord3\fsp5\c&H5C2D77&\3c&HB39188&\an7\move(391.333,92.667,391.333,27.334)}洞天水族馆特制原创刨冰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:23.22,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康平剧体 Std W7\bord5\fsp7\c&H9E2520&\3c&HB49188&\move(634.666,263.333,634.666,198)}特别菜单
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:23.22,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康平剧体 Std W7\bord3\fsp7\c&H5B2B0C&\3c&HB49188&\move(957.333,332.666,957.333,267.333)}斑嘴环企鹅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:23.22,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康平剧体 Std W7\bord3\fsp7\c&H222E19&\3c&HB49188&\move(286.666,443.333,286.666,378)}黄缘闭壳龟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:23.22,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康平剧体 Std W7\bord3\fsp7\c&H225379&\3c&HB49188&\move(921.333,550,921.333,484.667)}眼斑双锯鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:23.22,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康平剧体 Std W7\bord3\fsp7\c&H915847&\3c&HB49188&\move(349.333,644.667,349.333,579.334)}黄尾梅鲷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:23.22,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康平剧体 Std W7\bord3\fsp7\c&H3B6877&\3c&HB49188&\move(1058,730,1058,663)}珠蝴蝶鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.13,0:19:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.41,0:19:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你选个喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.13,0:19:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐就会给你做秘藏的刨冰哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.56,0:19:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我要眼斑双锯鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.22,0:19:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,斑嘴环企鹅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.52,0:19:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.23,0:19:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.20,0:19:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,太强了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.43,0:19:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,帅呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.35,0:19:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么  给我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.31,0:19:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,用动物的名字下单  真是新颖的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.99,0:19:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是乌冬妹想出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.98,0:19:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,「为了让大家留下水族馆的开心记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.59,0:20:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,要做出难以忘却的刨冰」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.68,0:20:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然菜单上没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.30,0:20:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,能做躄鱼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.71,0:20:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  我来试试
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.33,0:20:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.73,0:20:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.82,0:20:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.67,0:20:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那鱼是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.39,0:20:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,阿海的推荐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.26,0:20:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,如何入门并不重要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.04,0:20:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,只要能让大家对海洋生物产生兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.75,0:20:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.85,0:20:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也回到岗位上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.83,0:20:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.31,0:20:42.76,Comment,,0,0,0,,欢迎品尝洞天水族馆原创刨冰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.67,0:22:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,大感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.35,0:22:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这次可是全靠乌冬妹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.48,0:22:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,真是谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.72,0:22:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,没事没事  我也做得很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.72,0:22:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,刨冰大受好评  被人发上了Pensta
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.53,0:22:28.28,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正兰亭细黑_GBK\fs20\bord0\an7\c&H555757&\frz356\b0\pos(510,510.666)}洞天水族馆的原创刨冰黄缘闭壳龟口味，比我想象中还要\N龟里龟气的，笑翻了ww
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.95,0:22:30.03,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正兰亭细黑_GBK\fs20\bord0\an7\c&H555757&\b0\frz355.5\pos(507.334,522.666)}仿佛在说「你敢吃我吗」的黄尾梅鲷刨冰，吃得很满足哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.70,0:22:31.53,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正兰亭细黑_GBK\fs20\bord0\an7\c&H555757&\b0\frz355.5\pos(714.001,592)}附近的水族馆在卖这样的东西!\N再现了珠蝴蝶鱼的模样，太棒了!\N孩子们也很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.84,0:22:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,要是能乘着势头  客人增多就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.57,0:22:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.34,0:22:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我也要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.33,0:22:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我想为将来自己的店  多学习下料理
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.49,0:22:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,自己的店?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.11,0:22:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,自己开店的话  想怎么做都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.70,0:22:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,可以做多多的原创菜单
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.91,0:22:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,内饰也照我的意思来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.84,0:23:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,梦想在膨胀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.12,0:23:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我要当常客第一号
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.14,0:23:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,月美  给我一份芒果炖肉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.22,0:23:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  芒果炖肉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.97,0:23:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,哎  不是普通炖肉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.03,0:23:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,趁我没改变主意  赶快
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.64,0:23:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.92,0:23:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这么甜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.77,0:23:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,凭这个是开不了店的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.68,0:23:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你…你听见了?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.32,0:23:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,说得那么大声  肯定听到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.69,0:23:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,太羞耻了
